        <p>至此就可看到菜单项了<br /> <a href="http://7xo8d8.com1.z0.glb.clouddn.com/2015/11/Copyright_plugin_3.png-logcopyright"><img src="http://7xo8d8.com1.z0.glb.clouddn.com/2015/11/Copyright_plugin_3.png-logcopyright" alt="Copyright_plugin_3" width="401" height="430" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-221" /></a><br /> 开始添加设置页面，主要代码如下</p> 
