        <p>点击新加的菜单，可以显示出来一个页面了，我们可以在这里设置版权信息文本。<br /> <a href="http://7xo8d8.com1.z0.glb.clouddn.com/2015/11/Copyright_plugin_4.png-logcopyright"><img src="http://7xo8d8.com1.z0.glb.clouddn.com/2015/11/Copyright_plugin_4-426x450.png-logcopyright" alt="Copyright_plugin_4" width="426" height="450" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-220" srcset="http://7xo8d8.com1.z0.glb.clouddn.com/2015/11/Copyright_plugin_4-426x450.png-logcopyright 426w, http://7xo8d8.com1.z0.glb.clouddn.com/2015/11/Copyright_plugin_4.png-logcopyright 504w" sizes="(max-width: 426px) 100vw, 426px" /></a><br /> 另外还有如下代码需要修改</p> 
